          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What is the best AI website builder for healthcare providers?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Squarespace is best for most healthcare providers due to professional templates, Acuity scheduling integration, and polished appearance. Doctors, therapists, and medical practices benefit from the trustworthy design and patient-friendly features. Wix offers more features including Wix Bookings for appointment scheduling, which works well for dentists and specialists needing more functionality. Durable is fastest for wellness providers who need quick setup with built-in CRM. For HIPAA compliance, you'll need specialized solutions - most AI builders can handle general information and scheduling, but protected health information requires healthcare-specific platforms.</p>
